text: Ithocritus multimaculatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Maurice Pic in 1934. It is known from Vietnam.BioLib.cz - Ithocritus multimaculatus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1934
